description: Kingston's DataTraveler GE9 is a capless, ultra-thin Flash drive with a 24-carat gold-plated casing. It adds style to portable storage in a form factor that lets you easily use several drives side-by-side in USB ports. This stylish drive was designed by industrial designer Arman Emami, who won the Red Dot Industrial Design contest and is a multiple winner of this award. Its trendsetting design makes a strong impression. DataTraveler GE9 is backed by a five-year warranty, free technical support and the legendary reliability that makes Kingston the most trusted name in memory, with 25 years as the world's independent memory leader.
title: Kingston Digital DataTraveler GE9 2.0 (DTGE9/8GBZ)
